document_data.mainbody:
Szantels Ropes, Cords, Chains, and Mesh was a shop in the city of Arabel in Cormyr in the late 14 century DR.
The store was located on the northern side of the High Road where it intersected the East Way and Calantars Way in the center of the city. It sat directly west of Hawks Perch Trading House and across the street from the shop of Dazniir Relharphin, the wheelwright.
